Knowledge Center
U-Gold Account

This is an integrated savings and current account that allows the customer to make payment of cheques and dividend warrants into the account as well as issue specially designed cheques drawn on the account to third parties. These cheques can however only be cashed across the Bank's counters.

Benefits

  • Earns attractive rate of interest
  • Flexible management of funds
  • No clearing transaction cost for cheques issues
